# Privacy Policy for Auto Screen Brightness

**Effective Date:** January 11, 2026

**Auto Screen Brightness** (“we”, “our”, or “the App”) is committed to protecting your privacy. This Privacy Policy explains how we handle any information collected when you use our app.

## Information We Collect
Auto Screen Brightness does **not collect, store, or transmit any personal information**. The app only interacts with your **local device settings** to adjust screen and overlay brightness based on schedules you configure.

## How We Use Information
The app uses access to **display brightness settings** solely to:  
- Automatically adjust screen brightness according to user-defined schedules.  
- Control overlay brightness for comfort and usability.  

No data is sent to external servers or third parties.

## Permissions
To perform brightness adjustments, the app may request the **runFullTrust capability** to run a trusted background process on your device. This process only accesses system-level display settings and **does not access personal files or network resources**.

## Security
We take reasonable measures to ensure your device settings are handled safely. The app does **not transmit or share any personal data**.

## Children’s Privacy
This app is not intended for children under 13. We do not knowingly collect personal information from children.

## Changes to This Privacy Policy
We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. The latest version will always be available within the app or on our official website.
